---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import HeroImage from "@components/HeroImage.astro";
import Description from "@components/Description.astro";
import Table from "@components/Table.astro";
import TableRow from "@components/TableRow.astro";
import PlatformLink from "@components/PlatformLink.astro";

import DescriptionPicture from "@components/DescriptionPicture.astro";

import image1 from "@assets/games/factorio/picture1.jpg";
import image2 from "@assets/games/factorio/picture2.png";
---

<style>
  :root {
    --header-image-hue: 175deg;
    --header-image-brightness: 0.4;
    --header-image-saturation: 5;
  }
</style>

<Layout
  title="Gummientchen - Factorio"
  description="Join Gummientchen on a gaming odyssey like no other. From dominating battlefields to unraveling epic quests, Gummientchen explores pixel realms, leaving no virtual stone unturned."
  heading="Factorio"
  subheading="Everything is infinite. Except time and UPS."
  minimal="true"
>
  <HeroImage svg="factorio" />
  <Table title="My Stats">
    <TableRow component="Playtime">623 hours (18.08.2023)</TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Platform">Steam</TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Playing with">
      <PlatformLink
        linktext="Raron"
        linkhref="https://steamcommunity.com/id/raron1"
        iconname="steam"
      /> /
      <PlatformLink
        linktext="Damheat"
        linkhref="https://steamcommunity.com/id/damhaet"
        iconname="steam"
      />
    </TableRow>
  </Table>
  <Description>
    <p>Welcome to the mesmerizing world of Factorio – an extraordinary game.</p>

    <p>
      Embark on an interstellar journey as a brilliant engineer, stranded on an
      alien planet, armed with nothing but resourcefulness and determination.
      Your mission? Transform this enigmatic realm into a symphony of industry,
      creation, and survival. As the conductor of this remarkable cosmic
      orchestra, you must craft tools, machines, and technologies, all while
      fending off the indigenous creatures of this strange world.
    </p>

    <p>
      Factorio, the crown jewel of construction and management simulations,
      beckons you to sculpt a thriving factory paradise. Master the art of
      resource-gathering with real-time strategy, as you design intricate
      systems to automate mining, processing, and assembly. The blueprint system
      grants you the power to duplicate entire factory sections, turning your
      efforts into masterpieces of efficiency.
    </p>

    <DescriptionPicture
      src={image1}
      alt="Powerful rocket launching from within a dense forest in Factorio, soaring triumphantly from its launch silo amidst the vibrant greenery. Wube©"
    />

    <p>
      But beware, for as your factory grows, so does the ire of the planet's
      ferocious inhabitants – Biters, Spitters, and Worms. Pollution fuels their
      aggression, demanding a delicate balance between progress and harmony.
      Defend your creations using tanks, turrets, and your ingenious weaponry,
      evolving your arsenal to counter ever-adapting foes.
    </p>

    <p>
      Feel the exhilaration of cooperation in multiplayer mode, where you and
      your friends can collaborate, compete, and share blueprints in the
      ultimate factory-building frenzy. And for those with a creative itch, the
      modding community beckons, inviting you to craft your own stories,
      systems, and visual transformations.
    </p>

    <p>
      Witness the birth of Factorio through a labor of love from the minds at
      Wube Software. From humble beginnings to galactic triumph, this game has
      matured into a phenomenon, enchanting over three million players with its
      intricate gameplay and captivating visuals.
    </p>

    <DescriptionPicture
      src={image2}
      alt="Captivating artwork depicting a colossal alien worm baring its multitude of razor-sharp teeth in a menacing display, adding an extra layer of intrigue to the mysterious world of Factorio. Wube©"
    />

    <p>
      Now is your chance to immerse yourself in a universe where science and
      whimsy coalesce, as you design, defend, and dominate your way to becoming
      an industrial titan. Let Factorio be your beacon of strategic brilliance,
      where rubber ducks and rocket launches collide in a cosmic ballet of
      construction and chaos.
    </p>

    <p>
      Join the ranks of devoted engineers who have paved their path to the
      stars. Unleash your inner architect, tactician, and adventurer in the
      world of Factorio. Get ready to build, automate, and conquer – all with a
      rubber ducky by your side.
    </p>
  </Description>
  <Table title="Information about the Game">
    <TableRow component="Developer">Wube Software</TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Publisher">Wube Software</TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Release Date">14.08.2020</TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Genre">
      Factory simulation, real-time strategy
    </TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Official Website">
      <PlatformLink
        linktext="factorio.com"
        linkhref="https://www.factorio.com/"
        iconname=""
      />
    </TableRow>
    <TableRow component="Steam Store Page">
      <PlatformLink
        linktext="Factorio on Steam"
        linkhref="https://store.steampowered.com/app/427520/Factorio/"
        iconname="steam"
      />
    </TableRow>
  </Table>
</Layout>
